content_html:
Kathmandu, September 21

Those injured during the Gen-Z Protest staged a sit-in at the gate of Singha Durbar.

They had attempted to enter Singha Durbar to submit a memorandum to the Prime Minister Sushila Karki.

However, after security personnel barred their entry, they staged the sit-in at the gate itself.

The post Injured Gen Z protesters stage sit-in at Singha Durbar gate (Photos) appeared first on OnlineKhabar English News.
